prior to https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/pull/113151, I couldn't reproduce nopConverter seeing items with unset metadata in this scenario

after https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/pull/113151, nopConverter frequently sees items with unset metadata in this scenario

